description:
Join Moomin, in their wonderful adventures, from the 1950`s. 
 
In the first volume of the series, we are introduced to Moomintroll, Sniff, and other characters. The Moomin family also winds up to a lonely island.
In this volume, Moomin are menaced by a comet (this story is a second version of a same kind of story that was published before), and Moomintroll gets a golden tail.
Moomin stay up during winter (an old Moomin tradition is to sleep during winter), and Moomintroll goes to sea.
In this volume, Snofsan gets a large diamond and starts to live like a dukess, Sniff gets a sports-shop and Moomin get frightened, because there`s a vampire bat on the loose.

At last, it's the final showdown between Spider Jerusalem and the corrupt president of the United States in this new printing of the title collecting TRANSMETROPOLITAN #55-60, along with the specials I HATE IT HERE and FILTH OF THE CITY.
name: Vol. 10

description: In this new edition collecting issues #49-54, Spider Jerusalem turns up some startling evidence and a sole witness to President Callahan's depravity. The problem will be getting the word out before the President's massive forces black out everything – and everyone – involved.
name: Volume 9

description: A DC ONE MILLION tie-in! In an isolated, idyllic society a thousand years after the events of DC ONE MILLION, three teenagers unearth the forbidden legacy of the Legion of Super-Heroes. But if these future youths dare to rekindle the Legion flame, their families, friends and neighbors may destroy them!
name: 1,000 Years Later
